On-Demand :  Request when you want it 
             Flexible and Most Expensive 
             Use and Throw ! 
             Ideal for : 
                    -   A web application which receives spikey traffic 
                    -   A batch program which has unpredicatable runtime and cannot be interrupted 
                    -   A batch program being moved from on premises to cloud for the first time. 



Spot : Quote the maximum price 
       Cheapest (up to 90% off ) BUT NO Guarantees 




